reviews.text: A Portuguese restaurant with great views and a well-decorated and laid-out place. Food is good but not too special, and one needs to create their own balanced dishes as the mains from the grill don't come with sides. Can be very heavy in certain tastes, and a bit pricey as one needs to order so many separate items for their meal. Well worth a try, but your mileage might vary.
Penny , the assistant manager is the best. He will suggest you the best prices and options. 😂. Look for him

Good view.
Seats and tables were 
comfortable. Food and service of waiters need improvement.

Great view on the Victoria, but food is bad. I had lobster bisque which taste bland and very tiny bits of lobster. 

I then ordered the sirloin medium rare. Not sure what sauce they gave, just salty brown. No sides except a garlic.

I will not visit this restaurant again.

Everything was prepared well from the appetizers to each of the main dishes. The paella rice was undercooked and dry. Otherwise, a well rounded meal made from quality ingredients at a decent standard for this price point.

reviews.text:
一般，食環境吧。
春雞好似比較好味實惠，有少許炭香，加上薯條，都十分飽肚。加錢再配沙律吧，有多種菜蔬菇茄和少量點甜品
麵包粉就好一般。魷魚無味又唔熱，蝦也只是一般的新鮮度，麵包粉似糊狀，賣相不吸引，入口味道也沒見得很好。
百多元有一半是用在享受維港景色了，食物沒什麼特別好味。

牛肋羅宋湯足料，有牛味，茄膏都唔係用好多，但偏淡肉湯味。

海鮮意粉，足料，味道不過不失，葡汁的椰糖味好出。

慢煮牛肋寬條麵，啲牛原來係粒上，有特色但不討好。
啲野好食又好飲，再加埋無敵海景價格正路，係哩頭來講係不錯既選擇！

A Portuguese restaurant with great views and a well-decorated and laid-out place. Food is good but not too special, and one needs to create their own balanced dishes as the mains from the grill don't come with sides. Can be very heavy in certain tastes, and a bit pricey as one needs to order so many separate items for their meal. Well worth a try, but your mileage might vary.
침사추이 심포니 오브 라이트 보러 왔다가 중국인들이 노동절이라 너무 많이 몰려 대충보고 저녁먹으러 왔습니다. 까르보나라 파스타와 시그니쳐 해산물 필라(복음밥종류)를 주문 했는데. 까르보나라 스파게티는 그런대로 먹을 정도. 그러나 시그니쳐라는 해산물 볶음밥은 역겨워서 두숟가락 먹고 나왔습니다. 별한개도 아깝네요.
坐近窗前，可欣賞迷人夜景，倍增浪漫氣氛，衹是食物分量較少，味道及烹調少了些心思，質量少了吸引力

reviews.text: We had a late lunch here, so my wife and I were only one two tables. The two wait staff were fabulous. The food was terrific. Their signature dish, the steak with the egg on top, is a masterpiece. Have it with rice to sop up the sauce. Decor is simple but relaxing and clean. Music was at just the right level, and it's one of the rare times I've actually felt it contributed to the meal. Reasonable price for quality dishes. An excellent experience all round.

Food not really good. The bread is ok by itself but with the beef sandwich? And the fries are very simple to make and they did not do a good job. I heard from the other ppl st the table, the rice don't have much flavor. The only reason this place gets 2 stars is because the way they present the food is good. And the decorations and setup of the restaurant.
Very nice place for friends gathering, we spent a wonderful night there with good food and all laughters. Will be better if they provide free tap water and hot water

Sophisticated restaurant serving tasty albeit rather pricey food. Service is friendly and authentic. Seating is cosy but still comfortable. Slightly disappointing that they don't serve water - you must pay for bottled water. Their signature steak in creamy sauce topped with a friend egg (a traditional Portuguese dish apparently) was mediocre, but their clams in white wine sauce and octopus salad were excellent.
so welcomed me! really appreciate that😍 and foods were also good😍 Visit Korea! then i will welcome you guys😙💛

시그니처라는 스테이크와 해물찜 그리고 에피타이저로 조개찜을 먹었습니다. 음식맛은 그냥 무난한 수준인데 가격이 너무 비쌉니다. 유럽도 아닌데 미네랄 워터를 유료로 파는 것도 좀... 마카오 물가를 생각해도 이 정도 가격대라면 더 좋은 대안들이 많을 것 같으니 가이드북이나 블로그 글만 보고 이 곳을 선택하지 않았으면 합니다.

【総評】☆☆☆
二階建てで、キャパはそこそこありました。
堅苦しくなく、気軽に入れるお店でした。
味は普通か少し美味しいかなというレベルで、コスパは若干悪い気がしますが、JCBカードで支払うと10%引きなので、そこはプラスでした。
日本の方が美味しい店が多いですが、旅行で価格が気にならなければ良いと思います。
《JCBカード：可》

【味】★★★
エビのガーリック炒め、ステーキの目玉焼きのせは普通に美味しかったが、感動するレベルではなかった。
タコの酢漬けとカニのペーストは、私の好みではなかったので、トータルとして普通になりました。
料理ではないですが、初めて『Super Bock黒』を飲みましたが、フルーティーな黒ビールで美味しかったです。何ならコレが一番美味しかったです(笑)
私は頼んでいませんが、他のお客さんや店員さんがサングリアを薦めていたので、オススメなのかもしれません。
【サービス】★★★★
とてもフレンドリーで、英語が話せない私たちにも優しくしてくれました！
【コスパ】★★
味を考えると少し高い気がします。
服務態度很好，麵包吃的出來是自己造的，也很好吃很香小麥味道，每份食物的份量都很足夠，不過價錢小貴，但作為遊客覺得整體上很好。

價格高，酒水要錢，牛排不錯，烤雞柴；最好吃的是海鮮燉飯；酒水不便宜，一定要點，口會渴
JCB卡打9折
